###############################################################################
#                                vtkExplicitDeformableModel                   #
###############################################################################


1. Introduction
---------------

The purpose of this library is to share the code related to a VTK journal
submission. It is also a subset of the vtkKinship library.

2. Build and install
--------------------

Build with CMake:
- A simple 'cmake /path/to/sources/' will generate a Makefile for compiling
  the core library vtkExplicitDeformableModel
- Using ccmake or cmake-gui, you can choose to build the examples related in the
  paper
- Using ccmake or cmake-gui and if you have a ParaView development version, you
  can also choose to build the ParaView plugin.

